text:
(Hmm... Rinze seems to have fallen asleep.
I want to let her rest, but we're short on time...)

Sorry for startling you.
Are you okay? You seem quite sleepy...

I apologize...
For my embarrassing behavior...

Ah, Rinze... If you're tired,
I'll adjust the schedule, so don't rush...

(...Did I push her too hard?
I'll adjust the schedule to ensure she can rest.)
